"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Having a strategy is important, but so is knowing when to adjust it. If your agency isn't evolving your marketing strategy based on data, you're wasting time and resources. A strong marketing strategy partner understands your customers, monitors, and optimizes. \\n\\n[https://www.google.com/search?rlz=1C1CHBF_enUS975US975&sxsrf=AOaemvIMqXXXrhBLI0pwwHLucIPGwLA2SA:1641462741516&q=Adaptech+Design+Company&ludocid=14131203778415956359&gsas=1&lsig=AB86z5XTfN_cP6kaNklFGqLzbmeC&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiFsvqc7Zz1AhXgmWoFHVh_BeEQoAJ6BAgLEAc](https://www.google.com/search?rlz=1C1CHBF_enUS975US975&sxsrf=AOaemvIMqXXXrhBLI0pwwHLucIPGwLA2SA:1641462741516&q=Adaptech+Design+Company&ludocid=14131203778415956359&gsas=1&lsig=AB86z5XTfN_cP6kaNklFGqLzbmeC&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiFsvqc7Zz1AhXgmWoFHVh_BeEQoAJ6BAgLEAc)\\n\\nOur expertise in generating data-driven, journey-based marketing strategies enables us to effectively serve clients in a wide range of industries.\\n\\n[https://adaptechdesign.com/](https://adaptechdesign.com/)\\n\\nTo attract an audience, you must first understand their requirements and challenges. We conduct thorough audience research to learn about the issues that audiences confront. Our team's competitive study analyzes the landscape to uncover areas where your company might gain an advantage in the market today.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/-KJw2QO-bamKzRdL6pMFt.png?height=500&width=1500)\\n\\nToday's audiences are empowered by linked technology but also swamped with marketing communications. It's more difficult than ever to be heard above the din.\\n\\nEven conversion-focused brands must consider establishing and sustaining a devoted audience in order to avoid commoditization or disruption. You need a story to establish that kind of brand. And a strategy was required to shape that tale.\\n\\nAdaptech Design Company builds marketing strategies that generate extraordinary results by leveraging our digital knowledge, analytics expertise, and creative skills. In a disruptive landscape, our team combines the art and science of strategy, capturing opportunities through practical insights and compelling narrative.\\n\\n*HENDERSON, R. (2019, January 10). Adaptech Design | Digital Marketing & Design. Adaptech Design | Digital Marketing & Design. adaptechdesign.com.*\",\"timestamp\":1641464111,\"title\":\"Adaptech Design Company\"},\"digest\":\"nIQ1IDcpwzvTW7nG0PeCyH9saCVlC6LU7aMIuJzx6PU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd0C23AA1E5648AadF8F558F6B4Ef7F00a1368257\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ki3NBEx5umXjIL0zldJvQJGkyc6bhI3exVB4SsvC9ic\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5eP7wwbR1u38S8aqVrzfE9qtrqtcZYn7iIpexlCAQ2U\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"p7kjOv8Pwg05vvgajfR2xXkaTAMgnjaq-MGgXpS8aSdXoVm8ptWoOs58jpJ6BllPauivqveHPon11QGk8YOPxA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3558c9de4e457883f4d471a0deabb1fb8d5eba4c803c84bbfeb5045b5bc5e6af6263c427b8984422b6d4a0971c9b8bdc9efe92509d8b0b15ddc30a85cff213c11c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ki3NBEx5umXjIL0zldJvQJGkyc6bhI3exVB4SsvC9ic\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5eP7wwbR1u38S8aqVrzfE9qtrqtcZYn7iIpexlCAQ2U\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"SSNm3FVlVHULLjW5eJOfTQzxo5m93AA0NMABaDbYEbE\"}"